title: Russia retaliates, expelling 60 U.S. diplomats
text:
Russia retaliates, expelling 60 U.S. diplomats Thursday, March 29, 2018 - 01:37 
The move - retaliation against Washington which expelled the same number of Russian diplomats over the poisoning of an ex Russian spy in England. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
